IMAPAccount work
Host <intel specific stuff>
User <work email>
AuthMechs <intel specific stuff>
PassCmd <intel specific stuff>
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore work-remote
Account work

MaildirStore work-local
Path ~/Mail/work/
Inbox ~/Mail/work/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel work
Far :work-remote:
Near :work-local:
# Include everything. Alternatively you can select the folders you're interested on
Patterns * "!All Mail"
Remove Both
SyncState *

# proton secondary config
IMAPAccount proton
Host <proton ip>
User <proton mail>
Port <proton port>
TLSType STARTTLS
CertificateFile <cert file>
Pass <proton bridge pass>

IMAPStore proton-remote
Account proton

MaildirStore proton-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/proton/
Inbox ~/Mail/proton/Inbox

Channel proton
Far :proton-remote:
Near :proton-local:
# Include everything. Alternatively you can select the folders you're interested on
Patterns * "!All Mail"
Create Near
Sync All
Expunge Both
SyncState *
